OL,5, A concert promoter for Little Mix      
OL,6, discriminated against three deaf       
OL,7, mothers when it failed to provide a    
OL,8, British Sign Language (BSL) interpreter
OL,9, for support acts, a judge has ruled.   
OL,11,FSally Reynolds, Sarah Cassandro and    
OL,12,FVictoria Nelson attended a concert in  
OL,13,FWest Sussex with their children, who   
OL,14,Fcan hear, in September 2017.           
OL,16,FThe women had requested an interpreter 
OL,17,Fso they could also enjoy the music.    
OL,19,FLHG Live offered carer tickets and said
OL,20,Fthey could bring their own interpreter.
